Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壯少將和雷文中將失蹤的事情有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她不會笨到留下證據
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他 我們的工作是掌握這個要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁那個女狐狸被中央都市的那些老虎圍住的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見 少將閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你居然在中央勤務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使了什麼門路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這難道不是實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛頭小子 挺會說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天來這裡有什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大總統閣下叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有一陣子回不了北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回不去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請務必一起吃頓飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你請客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到讓你破產為止也可以的話 我可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼吃飯就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 膽子和錢包都很小的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換 送您點花怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央都市有很多不錯的花店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 阿姆斯壯少將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說說關於雷文中將失蹤的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來無法隱藏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到閣下這樣的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然會把那種草莽的人放在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把他做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要那種人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留著那種大嘴巴的傢伙對閣下沒有任何好處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中將對妳說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及閣下的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種沒問他的事情 都告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在聽了那些話之後還接受了傳訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 為了來取那個傻子坐的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 給妳一把椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換 布里克斯要塞由我的人來統治 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請自由處置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我精心培養的屈強之兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會讓閣下滿意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倔強地爬上來吧 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少將自己進了虎穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也成了他們的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他們不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使主人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是一塊可以在同一意志下活動的巨大岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就是熊和虎的爭奪戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}燒瓶中的小人（人造人）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡空著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如妳所見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙得如果不邊吃邊幹就會跟不上進度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要記住的東西太多 也比較忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是閣下工作很快 讓我省了不少心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟不會偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這話題會變得無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說斯卡現在在北方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛力克兄弟也在北方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在和我同期的露西和伊安也在北方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會告訴我各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得今年春天北方與東方進行了次聯合軍事演習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃過好幾次邁爾斯少佐和帕卡尼亞大尉的虧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邁爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕卡尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾達和修加也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈博克 奧斯卡 邁克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤尼 諾拉 查理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次說了尤尼 然後是露西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤尼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是斯特林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑利姆·布拉德雷是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼不可能的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個中央都市到底會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那邊的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你就沒有稍微驚訝什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚訝的話 你會給我什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膽子大這點我倒是很欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說號碼 告訴我真名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 因為是奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有權利和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為所有物被轉讓和買賣的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉讓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是財產 權利等交給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你腦子真不好使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會從這種人這裡誕生 完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我血的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 說是要用在實驗上 取走不少…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你賦予了我血液 所以我出生在了這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然23號不是滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你取個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當自己是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取個神氣點的比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特奧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特奧弗拉斯托斯·博姆巴斯托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 太長的記不住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為腦子不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說我腦子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就叫 馮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馮·霍恩海姆怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馮·霍恩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個能記住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼法是…對了 你會讀書寫字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會那個也能幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隸的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想要自由和權利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想無法獲得作為人類的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作奴隸完結一生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就和這氣悶的燒瓶中是一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我給予你知識吧 馮·霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你什麼才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒瓶中的小人 叫我人造人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世間萬物 由一而生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終歸為一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 一就是全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全由一出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全中含一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如果不包含全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都化為無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經是位了不起的鍊金術師了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒有走出助手的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離主人的水平還差遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你賦予了我知識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才過上了好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很感謝主人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天和誰結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有家庭也不再是夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類真是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那樣通過交流才進行繁殖的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,種族便不能存續了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你的角度看也許很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭什麼的 同伴什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那些東西裡存在幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你的幸福是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 不說得很奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個能從這燒瓶裡出去的身體就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼達到權力和榮華頂端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會要往那個方面想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是陛下的御前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你繼續無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把那個燒瓶砸碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要破壞你們無法知道的知識源泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話就不必多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能還是不能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為衰老導致的焦躁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克塞魯克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我就告訴你長生不老的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼工程？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灌溉用水道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據國王的命令 要在全國張開水道網
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是克塞魯克塞斯王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們這些百姓的生活也想得很周到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不留 全殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點刻上血之紋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說北方的村子被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不留全被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前是西邊的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼人幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您期盼的鍊成陣終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 能長生不老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王能變得長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可以說是世紀性的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是長生不老？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說在中心的我們不會受害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍊成陣真正的中心是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所站的這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用了在我體內的你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們打開了門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血脈相連的家人 霍恩海姆喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 你和我是一切的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維蘭德 梅希帝魯德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊因麥爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼 梅悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰？回我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的靈魂都被抽走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個身體 還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用你的血之資訊 製作了一個容器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能用自己的身體走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人造人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為給予我血的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你名字 教給你知識
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予你不會衰老的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會衰老？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把意識集中到自己身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成為不死之身而作為交換的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家所有人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過有一半歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你的協助 霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然是愛德和阿爾的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是妳 沒想到是我兒子們的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上給妳藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給妳看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微接觸過一點醫學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？這怎麼會沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西格先生 去叫一輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳見過真理了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳犧牲了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子裡的…被取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想復活死去的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳肚子被刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 呼吸變得輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被取走的臟器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妳罪孽的證明 沒辦法取回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微整理了一下妳的肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把血的流向弄得順暢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米小姐 妳還不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有叫做馮·霍恩海姆這個人之形狀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哲學家之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大聖藥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如賢者之石有著多個名字一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形狀不一定是石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬可先生拿著的是半液體狀的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利的是礦石狀的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小就這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說蘊藏了很大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為是更大的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有見過比小石頭的尺寸更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是非常大的賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計要使用數量非常龐大的人類為材料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的話 還真不想見到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要付出同等的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是鍊金術的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是人世間的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第41話 地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年追求的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了作為代價的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:23.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}無止境的旅途中  止步不前之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:29.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我們深深地歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:37.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放開了緊握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是現在已經沒有什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:52.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}連接心靈之間那堅固的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:58.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}決不會被斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:07.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}繼續尋求 終於找到了
